sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>ChatbotPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>ChatSendMessageView
    participant Bot as ATT&CK-Aware Engine
    participant Ctx as _build_alert_context()
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Ask ATT&CK-related question
    FE->>API: POST /api/chat/send/ {session_id, message}
    API->>DB: ChatMessage.objects.create(session, role="user", content=message)
    API->>Ctx: _build_alert_context(user_environment)
    Ctx->>DB: Alert.objects.filter(environment=env).order_by("-timestamp")[:10]
    DB-->>Ctx: Recent alerts with MITRE mappings
    Ctx-->>API: Alert context summary
    API->>Bot: _fallback_response(message, alert_context)
    Bot->>Bot: Match MITRE technique patterns
    Bot->>Bot: Generate ATT&CK-enriched response
    Bot-->>API: Enhanced response with technique references
    API->>DB: ChatMessage.objects.create(session, role="assistant", content=response)
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {response, session_id}
    FE-->>U: Display response with ATT&CK technique links
